read/457077\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/457077</a><br />\n民國復興：幾時開始，連登性無能都可以推上神枱？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/460016\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/460016</a></strong></span>"},{"pid":"4528419534cb767fdb80f7fde25f26fe05022651","tid":461211,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T12:06:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>美國人又想撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n法蘭西撚完又俾美帝撚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19b714c2b8beca8aa75bc0d20d144e79b02c8d2e","tid":461211,"uid":98289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T12:18:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>美國人又想撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n法蘭西撚完又俾美帝撚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n侵遲d 送吓高帽<br />\n成個支那又會high 晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f39a10aa0e1050af9fe03f6b7ca4e7d3979675b","tid":461211,"uid":2654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T12:26:00.000Z","msg":"唔通爭住話自己勁咩 你咁威咪俾你贏囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到時一睇底牌咪分高低<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24449dca4faac3b23bdfb3e407b50aae8d16be50","tid":461211,"uid":34622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T13:54:28.000Z","msg":"冷戰個時蘇聯都比美國吹奏過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fabc34dea86aafc6b287a614aae7d0964c6b7aac","tid":461211,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T14:12